This paper deals with wireless communication networks and their security, which falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) categories. The paper also discusses the use of cooperative jamming, which is a technique used in cryptography and security (cs.CR). The use of multiple antennas is also discussed, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and systems and control (cs.SY) categories.
